OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry and cloudy,
OL,6,Foccasional rain across the Trossachs.
OL,7,FSome bright or sunny spells possible
OL,8,Facross the Central Belt and Fife.
OL,9,FBrisk southerly winds along the Angus
OL,10,Fcoast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be mainly
OL,13,Fdry. Then remaining mostly dry and
OL,14,Fcloudy overnight although some
OL,15,Foccasional rain possible across the
OL,16,FTrossachs and western Tayside. Mild.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with rain at
OL,19,Ftimes across the west, mainly dry in
OL,20,Fthe east although patchy rain
OL,21,Fdeveloping here later. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
